    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 credibility matrix for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. Discretization error and numerical solver error factors both achieved levels exceeding requirements, providing additional confidence. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions.",
